eparaz |first=Mike |work=[[GamesRadar]] |publisher=[[Future plc]] |date=16 June 2011 |accessdate=20 March 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110616024315/http://www.gamesradar.com/ps2/f/battle-of-the-gta-clones/a-2007032712758324075/g-2005120719070657885742 |archivedate=16 June 2011 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"IGN Benzies\">{{cite web |url=http://ign.com/articles/2001/02/23/grand-theft-auto-3-interview-with-dma |title=Grand Theft Auto 3: Interview with DMA |last=Perry |first=Douglass |work=[[IGN]] |publisher=[[Ziff Davis]] |date=22 February 2001 |accessdate=19 March 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160420073028/http://www.ign.com/articles/2001/02/23/grand-theft-auto-3-interview-with-dma |archivedate=20 April 2016 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"IGN Benzies DMA\">{{cite web |url=http://ign.com/articles/2001/10/03/an-interview-with-dmas-les-benzies |title=An Interview With DMA's Les Benzies |last=Perry |first=Douglass C. |date=3 October 2001 |accessdate=9 April 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414151927/http://www.ign.com/articles/2001/10/03/an-interview-with-dmas-les-benzies |archivedate=14 April 2016 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"IGN Cars\">{{cite web |url=http://ign.com/articles/2002/05/13/the-cars-of-grand-theft-auto-iii |title=The Cars of Grand Theft Auto III |last=Perry |first=Douglass C. |work=[[IGN]] |publisher=[[Ziff Davis]] |date=13 May 2002 |accessdate=19 March 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221220757/http://www.ign.com/articles/2002/05/13/the-cars-of-grand-theft-auto-iii |archivedate=21 February 2014 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"IGN Characters\">{{cite web |url=http://ign.com/articles/2001/08/29/the-characters-of-grand-theft-auto-iii-2 |title=The Characters of Grand Theft Auto III |last=Perry |first=Douglass C. |date=29 August 2001 |accessdate=9 April 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160420065841/http://www.ign.com/articles/2001/08/29/the-characters-of-g